data.description: Get a $5,000 credit towards closing costs! Charming patio home located in the highly desirable Creekside neighborhood of Heron River. Built by Oakmont Signature Homes, this single level home features upgrades throughout, including shiplap walls, hardwood flooring, quartz countertops, Bosch appliances, and a stone fireplaces flaked by custom built in cabinetry. Front bedroom has vaulted ceilings and large windows looking out the front of the house. Master suite includes separate tub and walk in shower. Large office located in a private corner of the house makes working from home enjoyable. Fully fenced backyard with covered patio. Living in this community includes access to the pool, pickleball, tennis, and basketball courts, as well as access to the community center and gym. HOA dues also include landscaping services, snow removal, and fiber-optic internet.
